        "latex": "Soit $u_n(x) = (-1)^n\\ln\\left(1+\\frac x{n(1+x)}\\right)$ et\n$f(x) = \\sum_{n=1}^\\infty u_n(x)$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(u_n(x) = (-1)^n\\ln\\left(1+\\frac x{n(1+x)}\\right)\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(x) = \\sum_{n=1}^\\infty u_n(x)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
