        "html": "<p>CSA <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Rightarrow  |R_n(x)| \\le |u_{n+1}(x)| \\le\n             \\ln\\left(1+\\frac1{n+1}\\right)\\)</span>. Non, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\|u_n\\|_\\infty = \\ln\\left(1+\\frac1n\\right)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
